{"tid":1420790,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成的角色?","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:53:50.000Z","uid":289924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c4e977d842300ce6caed327f027dfae360279f","tid":1420790,"uid":289924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"關於曾鈺成過去兩個月的一些訪問。<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-12<br />\n立法會自我規範功能徹底崩潰 「直上大會」是唯一打破僵局方法<br />\n&quot;...立法會前主席曾鈺成今早（12日）於無綫節目《講清講楚》表示，事件充分說明立法會自我約制及自我規範功能已「徹底崩潰」，現時雙方已很難作出讓步，唯一打破僵局方法是直接將草案提上立法會大會審議。...&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190512/s00001/1557636164722/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E9%88%BA%E6%88%90-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%B9%E5%BA%95%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0-%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B4%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190512%2Fs00001%2F1557636164722%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2588%25BA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%25AF%2584%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25BE%25B9%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0-%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2594%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%2583%25B5%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=a2290342\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190512%2Fs00001%2F1557636164722%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%25