F%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190524%2Fs00001%2F1558692332464%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%25AE%2580&h=5b7da2a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190524/s00001/1558692332464/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96%E3%80%91%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%8C%E8%AE%80</a><br />\n(來自:明報網站)<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-03<br />\n【逃犯條例】曾鈺成倡8．31框架外重啟政改 籲特首考慮特赦年輕人<br />\n&quot;...他說，判決之後，行政長官有可能考慮整件事由什麼引發，可能是更深層次的矛盾，而在事件中，若赦免這些年輕人，會對整個社會有好處，所以出於公眾利益考慮，而作特赦決定。...&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/article/20190703/special/1562162062351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fspecial%2F1562162062351&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=aad53c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fspecial%2F1562162062351&h=694294a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/article/20190703/special/1562162062351</a><br />\n(來自:明報網站)<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-04 至今<br />\n勇武參予人數越來越多，也越來越勇武。<br />\n(來自:個人觀察)<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-08<br />\n換人都無人做得比林鄭好 反送中成特區歷來最大危機<br />\n&quot;...又認為即使換人，亦無人可以做得比林鄭月娥好。...&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065513&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=ce62e59d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065513&h=0f9911f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065513</a><br />\n(來自:獨立媒體)<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n以上訪問和個人觀察只是表述發生的序，並不代表有其因果關係。<br />\n我個人對曾鈺成的印象，在建制派當中，算係比較正面。最近少了見到他在任何訪問上。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我支持成立獨立調查委員會。"},{"pid":"71d48db3cf20d5cd875e4c1de554950b7ead1364","tid":1420790,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"都係賣港 不過有光環"}]}